  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once a novelist, Vincent Marlow was forced to abandon his writing after being falsely accused. Then one day, he receives a letter from Sofia, asking him to find her missing younger brother—who disappeared in the place connected to the case that ruined his life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/46549d2c0da4cf6159fbd502a27c1c97.poster.avif?t=1772610043\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/46549d2c0da4cf6159fbd502a27c1c97.webm?t=1772610043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/46549d2c0da4cf6159fbd502a27c1c97.mp4?t=1772610043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unknown - Raven Field is the first Episode in the Unknown series, a gripping mystery adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Storyline: Uncover the lost memories of Sofia, Noah, and Olivia. Discover the family's forgotten past and the hidden secrets of Raven Field.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles and Riddles: Search the village for hidden clues and solve puzzles to uncover the mysteries of Raven Field.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interaction with Villagers: Engage with the villagers to get closer to the truth. Dive into their words and unravel the clues they hide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eerie Atmosphere: The suspenseful background music and meticulously designed environments deepen the mystery of Raven Field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/a66879585ea7505ef899c86c08c91731.poster.avif?t=1772610043\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/a66879585ea7505ef899c86c08c91731.webm?t=1772610043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/a66879585ea7505ef899c86c08c91731.mp4?t=1772610043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once a novelist, Vincent Marlow was forced to abandon his writing after being falsely accused. Then one day, he receives a letter from Sofia, asking him to find her missing younger brother—who disappeared in the place connected to the case that ruined his life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/46549d2c0da4cf6159fbd502a27c1c97.poster.avif?t=1772610043\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/46549d2c0da4cf6159fbd502a27c1c97.webm?t=1772610043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/46549d2c0da4cf6159fbd502a27c1c97.mp4?t=1772610043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unknown - Raven Field is the first Episode in the Unknown series, a gripping mystery adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Storyline: Uncover the lost memories of Sofia, Noah, and Olivia. Discover the family's forgotten past and the hidden secrets of Raven Field.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles and Riddles: Search the village for hidden clues and solve puzzles to uncover the mysteries of Raven Field.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interaction with Villagers: Engage with the villagers to get closer to the truth. Dive into their words and unravel the clues they hide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eerie Atmosphere: The suspenseful background music and meticulously designed environments deepen the mystery of Raven Field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/a66879585ea7505ef899c86c08c91731.poster.avif?t=1772610043\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/a66879585ea7505ef899c86c08c91731.webm?t=1772610043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553670/extras/a66879585ea7505ef899c86c08c91731.mp4?t=1772610043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
